netbeans.org Web Content Translation Status

This page shows the status of translations of web content on netbeans.org. If you'd like to help, please read the localisation guide.

Translation Status Table

Please mouse-over links and cells in the table for additional information. Only languages with an active translation team are displayed - if you'd like to add your language to this table, please get in touch!

OK Green cells indicate the translation is up to date;
In Progress Yellow cells indicate there is somebody working on the page;
Help! Red cells indicate the translation is needed;
